    "homesec_5": {
      "type": "review-section",
      "blocks": {
        "4d17af36-87c9-45cb-ab53-d602a11a0415": {
          "type": "featured-review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Love the products",
            "quote_by": "Maree",
            "paragraph": "<p>Hey Goju. Love the products - The care in packaging, great customer service & supports local awesomeness.</p>"
          }
        },
        "0e5c11cd-c21b-4ea6-94b5-6e62b22c2ebc": {
          "type": "featured-review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "High vibes",
            "quote_by": "Flora",
            "paragraph": "<p>Best investment! Keeps you high vibe and so good for my over all wellbeing!</p>"
          }
        },
        "48f5574d-8901-443a-8bd7-ff55a6fc7149": {
          "type": "featured-review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Keeps my whole family healthy",
            "quote_by": "Charlotte",
            "paragraph": "<p>I don't just like these shots. I love them. They keep my whole family healthy and we love the sweet and spicy flavour!</p>"
          }
        },
        "93beb0e6-9c85-4834-988c-c07e04119a76": {
          "type": "featured-review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Love for Supershot",
            "quote_by": "Nathan",
            "paragraph": "<p>I loved the Supershot so much when I sampled it! Ordered a dozen and they just arrived so can’t wait to rip into them. <br/><br/>Best part is that it taste like an orange juice but with a healthy gingery kick to it. Exactly what I was after leading into winter.</p>"
          }
        },
        "f3f60b56-5f46-42e5-82e3-5192fec8d2e4": {
          "type": "featured-review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Seriously good",
            "quote_by": "Skye",
            "paragraph": "<p>This lasts me way longer than just the 8 shots. I take a 30ml shot, I also add to hot water and add some to soda waters - so, so good!</p>"
          }
        },
        "480e8ee1-807c-4aa8-b2e5-a609aa9f1521": {
          "type": "featured-review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Absolutely love it",
            "quote_by": "Rochelle",
            "paragraph": "<p>Tried these shot for the first time. I absolutely love it! Tastes great and not too overwhelming. <br/>Will definitely buy again.</p>"
          }
        },
        "28490cfe-553c-4e7d-b156-e61aad761b88": {
          "type": "featured-review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Good for the Body & Soul",
            "quote_by": "Julie",
            "paragraph": "<p>Love the Shots, so easy to use. Pop in my handbag for taking to the office... especially nice mixed with hot water for a good winter warm-up, plus knowing that they are extra good for the Body & Soul. xx</p>"
          }
        },
        "9afb97ec-032a-4b3a-9f49-4105f40447fb": {
          "type": "featured-review",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "Improving my immunity",
            "quote_by": "Vivienne",
            "paragraph": "<p>Love these shots! I take 30ml in the morning & again in the evening.  I feel it’s improving my immunity & menopause symptoms.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
